## AI Overviews reward clear answers and trusted context.

When AI summarizes search results, vague content becomes easier to ignore. Pages need clear structure, original value and enough context for both humans and machines.

This does not remove classic SEO work. It makes technical health, entity clarity and topical authority even more important.

## How to adapt

Answer specific questions, cite real expertise, keep pages easy to scan, add structured data where appropriate and avoid padding content just to chase word count.
